{"type": "article", "id": 30749, "title": "MacBook 收线器", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808204505ryPR59qmBE0ZsHFd.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>对 MacBook 用户来说，如何整齐地收纳充电器是一个不小的烦恼，由设计师 Joel Beebe 领导的团队为此特别设计了一款专用的收线器 Hula Wrap。这个由皮革制成的外套能够有效地保护 MagSafe，电源线可以缠绕在外并通过扣子固定，使用时只要打开扣子接上延长的 AC 电源线即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1031801104/hula-wrap-macbook-cable-organizer\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 25 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204523NkX1evphBHGyLmuF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204523Ef4TM8jxl9busZ2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.435294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808204523eQXIFzvkqLOfYahw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.519118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}